				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Modern Age" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="Modern_Age_(disambiguation)" title="Modern Age (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Modern Age (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
