dams" title="John Adams">John Adams</a>, <a href="Andrew_Jackson" title="Andrew Jackson">Andrew Jackson</a> and <a href="Jacksonian_Democracy" title="Jacksonian Democracy" class="mw-redirect">Jacksonian Democracy</a>, <a href="United_States_Republican_party" title="United States Republican party" class="mw-redirect">United States Republican party</a>, <a href="Joseph_Galloway" title="Joseph Galloway">Joseph Galloway</a>, <a href="Frederick_Jackson_Turner" title="Frederick Jackson Turner">Frederick Jackson Turner</a>, <a href="American_Anti-Slavery_Society" title="American Anti-Slavery Society">American Anti-Slavery Society</a>, <a href="../A._P._Herbert" title="A. P. Herbert">A. P. Herbert</a>, <a href="Rosa_Parks" title="Rosa Parks">Rosa Parks</a>, <a href="Jackie_Robinson" title="Jackie Robinson">Jackie Robinson</a>, <a href="Institute_of_Contemporary_History" title="Institute of Contemporary History">Institute of Contemporary History</a><sup class="plainlinks noprint Inline-Template" style="vertical-align:text-top;white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://toolserver.org/~dispenser/cgi-bin/dab_solver.py?page=Modern_history&editintro=Template:Disambiguation_needed/editintro&client=Template:Dn"><span title="Link needs disambiguation from June 2011">disambiguation needed</span></a></i>]</sup></dd>
